Richmond

Dorcas Louise Wolgemuth Baugher v. John O. Baugher. May 25, 1972. Record No. 7843.

Present, Snead, C.J., PAnson, Carrico, Gordon, Harrison and Harman, JJ.

Humes J. Franklin, Jr. (Franklin, Poindexter & Franklin, on brief), for appellant. Carter R. Allen (Allen & Dalton, on brief), for appellee.

Decree affirmed without opinion by equally divided Court.
